author: danielf
msg: Refactoring to put all inter block call handling and property handling in the BlockContext. Renamed the BlockEnvironmentHelper to BlockCallStack to better describe what it does. Putting the Servlet that actually do the work e.g. the SitemapServlet on the call stack instead of the BlockContext. BlockSource and the Block modules are updated to the new content on the call stack.
